Dialogue: 1,0:24:14.42,0:24:16.12,TitleNext,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}都是女生害羞什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.12,0:24:17.62,TitleNext,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}色氣擔當就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.62,0:24:19.37,TitleNext,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}這邊的身體搞定了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.37,0:24:21.57,TitleNext,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}晚歸的孩子要掛路燈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.57,0:24:23.18,TitleNext,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}水溫好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.10,0:24:26.94,TitleNext,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}下集 牧歌式的歡喜
