Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.19,0:00:43.50,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}於此世間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:46.76,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}何所思
