Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:10.12,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}啊 愈是真實
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.66,0:01:17.26,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}亦對人無比殘酷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:20.36,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}傲然怒放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.68,0:01:23.51,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}隨心所願
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.63,0:01:26.26,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}於這一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.50,0:01:29.76,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}傾注一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.14,0:01:35.27,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}令無限的群星亦黯然失色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.70,0:01:41.07,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}勇氣 由心而生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.63,0:01:51.12,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,500)}生存下去 無論何時
