Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.37,0:23:01.69,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}懷念在此相會的歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.93,0:23:03.63,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}心馳神往
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.97,0:23:05.71,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}日復一日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:08.85,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}時間如魔法般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.18,0:23:12.45,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}無論未來 現在 抑或過去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.73,0:23:14.70,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}都會成為追憶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.21,0:23:17.01,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}舒一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.11,0:23:19.71,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}慢慢深吸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.14,0:23:24.90,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}腦中浮現出相同的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.36,0:23:27.71,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}即便沒有約定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.87,0:23:30.51,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}心與心相通
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.87,0:23:32.62,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}一直一直
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.96,0:23:35.46,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}直到永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.71,0:23:39.42,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}每個人每個人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.50,0:23:42.54,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}都身纏無可替代的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.89,0:23:46.95,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}讓這片大地為之所染
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.28,0:23:50.73,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}每個人每個人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.73,0:23:53.31,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}都以不同的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.65,0:23:59.39,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}交相輝映
